  "title": "范式跃迁：LLM + EC 重构算法设计范式，华为&港城大夺冠 CVRP 国际顶级赛事",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA3MzI4MjgzMw==&mid=2651018881&idx=1&sn=b1a610953f1cb57a931918ee0a1d5254",
  "date": "2026-03-02 07:42:00",
